WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.852
MBAL is now a large evidence system; the output is a small set of checked decisions.

00:00:15.852 --> 00:00:34.198
The data map grew, but it also exposed the main gap: depth, not another model family.

00:00:34.198 --> 00:00:52.709
The updated story is a funnel: many inputs, many findings, very few promoted claims.

00:00:52.709 --> 00:01:12.490
Bacteria value is now measured as chronological warning: more episodes caught than AB411, with fewer scored false-alert days.

00:01:12.490 --> 00:01:29.991
CatBoost improves ranking, but the operational gain is too small to justify a champion swap.

00:01:29.991 --> 00:01:50.597
Forecast feeds pay only when fast carrier, headroom, and forecast skill all hold.

00:01:50.597 --> 00:02:08.123
Cold-start transfer is replicated on two independent networks: NSW Australia and the Texas Gulf.

00:02:08.123 --> 00:02:33.983
HAB/DA improved as a data and pilot lane, while the older broad DA overclaim is walked back.

00:02:33.983 --> 00:02:56.084
Algae value is targeted and scoped: free satellite prioritization, plus a small NE/Midwest onset edge.

00:02:56.084 --> 00:03:20.472
The one-system result is selective transfer from shared onset geometry, not a universal coupled predictor.

00:03:20.472 --> 00:03:40.608
The gate saves work: stop engine churn, reject untestable model families, keep useful data layers scoped.

00:03:40.608 --> 00:04:03.187
The updated MBAL story: bigger evidence base, narrower claims, clearer decisions.
